{"id": 59633, "date": "2025-09-10T04:00:55", "date_gmt": "2025-09-10T11:00:55", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=59633"}, "modified": "2026-05-24T14:55:51", "modified_gmt": "2026-05-24T21:55:51", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-september-10-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/09/10/kingdom-of-days-september-10-2/", "title": {"rendered": "September 10"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1971:\u00a0</strong>The Bruce Springsteen Band continues their residency at The Student Prince.</p>\n<p><strong>1978:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band bring the Darkness Tour to the Riverfront Coliseum in Cincinnati, where &#8220;Detroit Medley&#8221; makes its tour premiere. If you can&#8217;t make the show, you can listen to a two-hour radio special on Bruce premiering tonight on the King Biscuit Flower Hour.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21011\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1978-09-10a/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1978-09-10a.jpg?fit=2429%2C1315&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2429,1315\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1599030955&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1978-09-10a\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1978-09-10a.jpg?fit=758%2C410&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21011 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1978-09-10a.jpg?resize=758%2C410&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"410\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1978-09-10a.jpg?w=2429&amp;ssl=1 2429w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1978-09-10a.jpg?resize=300%2C162&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1978-09-10a.jpg?resize=1024%2C554&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1978-09-10a.jpg?resize=768%2C416&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1978-09-10a.jpg?resize=1536%2C832&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1978-09-10a.jpg?resize=2048%2C1109&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1978-09-10a.jpg?w=2274&amp;ssl=1 2274w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"29353\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1978-09-10b-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1978-09-10b.jpg?fit=659%2C1817&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"659,1817\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1599031052&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1978-09-10b\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1978-09-10b.jpg?fit=371%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-29353 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1978-09-10b.jpg?resize=659%2C1817&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"659\" height=\"1817\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1978-09-10b.jpg?w=659&amp;ssl=1 659w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1978-09-10b.jpg?resize=109%2C300&amp;ssl=1 109w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1978-09-10b.jpg?resize=371%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 371w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1978-09-10b.jpg?resize=557%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 557w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 659px) 100vw, 659px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"4240\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1978-0910/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1978-0910.jpg?fit=386%2C803&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"386,803\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1978-0910\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1978-0910.jpg?fit=386%2C803&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-4240 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1978-0910.jpg?resize=386%2C803&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"386\" height=\"803\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1978-0910.jpg?w=386&amp;ssl=1 386w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1978-0910.jpg?resize=144%2C300&amp;ssl=1 144w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 386px) 100vw, 386px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1979:\u00a0</strong>Bruce records &#8220;Mr. Outside&#8221; on a cassette recorder at home in Holmdel. He will release it 36 years later on\u00a0<em>The Ties That Bind: The River Collection</em>.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/PLa8TaCNM28?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=RDPLa8TaCNM28\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1981:\u00a0</strong>At Night Two on the River Tour at Chicago&#8217;s Rosemont Horizon, Bruce and the E Street Band play the one and only tour performance of &#8220;She&#8217;s the One,&#8221; its last appearance for almost seven years.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/zHxCBO7yzCI?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21013\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1981-09-10/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1981-09-10.jpg?fit=2433%2C685&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2433,685\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1599032267&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1981-09-10\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1981-09-10.jpg?fit=758%2C213&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21013 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1981-09-10.jpg?resize=758%2C213&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"213\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1981-09-10.jpg?w=2433&amp;ssl=1 2433w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1981-09-10.jpg?resize=300%2C84&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1981-09-10.jpg?resize=1024%2C288&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1981-09-10.jpg?resize=768%2C216&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1981-09-10.jpg?resize=1536%2C432&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1981-09-10.jpg?resize=2048%2C577&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1981-09-10.jpg?w=2274&amp;ssl=1 2274w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1984:\u00a0</strong>On a free day in between shows, Clarence appears as a guest on\u00a0<em>Late Night with David Letterman,\u00a0</em>and he performs a familiar song with the Red Bank Rockers.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/-kpB6TJCrhs?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21014\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1984-09-10/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1984-09-10.jpg?fit=2431%2C1906&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2431,1906\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1599033070&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1984-09-10\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1984-09-10.jpg?fit=758%2C594&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21014 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1984-09-10.jpg?resize=758%2C594&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"594\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1984-09-10.jpg?w=2431&amp;ssl=1 2431w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1984-09-10.jpg?resize=300%2C235&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1984-09-10.jpg?resize=1024%2C803&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1984-09-10.jpg?resize=768%2C602&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1984-09-10.jpg?resize=1536%2C1204&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1984-09-10.jpg?resize=2048%2C1606&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1984-09-10.jpg?w=2274&amp;ssl=1 2274w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1985:\u00a0</strong>Bruce shakes up the set list for Night Two in Miami on the Born in the U.S.A. Tour&#8211;no tour premieres, but several songs make their return after a month of unchanging sets.</p>\n<div id=\"v-Yx72G4DQ-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/Yx72G4DQ?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21015\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1985-09-10/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1985-09-10.jpg?fit=1155%2C1846&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1155,1846\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1599033301&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1985-09-10\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1985-09-10.jpg?fit=641%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21015 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1985-09-10.jpg?resize=758%2C1211&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"1211\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1985-09-10.jpg?w=1155&amp;ssl=1 1155w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1985-09-10.jpg?resize=188%2C300&amp;ssl=1 188w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1985-09-10.jpg?resize=641%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 641w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1985-09-10.jpg?resize=768%2C1227&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1985-09-10.jpg?resize=961%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 961w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"4244\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1985-0909/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1985-0909.jpg?fit=941%2C1300&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"941,1300\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1985-0909\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1985-0909.jpg?fit=741%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-4244 size-full\" src=\"ht